Package edu.ncsu.csc216.product_backlog.model.task

Class Task

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.product_backlog.model.task.Task
  • public class Task
extends java.lang.Object
    A Task Class represents a task tracked by the system. Task has six inner classes that each implement TaskState and each concrete state handles updating when given a command.
    Author:
    Veerendra Gottiveeti
